data.description: Incredible turnkey home in Meridian where extraordinary light & spaciousness combine to create a haven of tranquility. As you step inside, you'll immediately be captivated by the sheer brilliance of the home's design. The entire south wall of the home is adorned w/ expansive windows that bathe the living spaces in an abundance of natural light. The open kitchen boasts beautiful granite counters, custom cabinetry & SS appliances + a walk-in pantry that's bound to exceed your storage needs. You will enjoy a spacious dining nook & great room. The generous-sized primary features dual vanities, soaker tub, tiled shower & walk-in closet. One of the true gems of this home is the backyard setting, with no backyard neighbors your yard opens up to a scenic common space. The covered patio provides the perfect spot to savor the serenity of your surroundings. Minimal yard maintenance provides an overall "lock & leave" lifestyle. Enjoy a water softener, reverse osmosis, & home humidifier systems installed. Must see!!
